    "name": "酒馆21点 Blackjack Tavern",
    "steam_appid": 3262580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/1db63e89cec433c7255df436a9c1de09.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=128 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >写在前面</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炉石传说？杀戮尖塔？21点？再来1张？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准确的说是在杀戮尖塔肉鸽模式下的21点，棋盘模仿了炉石传说，如果你玩过它们，熟悉它们的游戏规则，那么这款游戏对你来说入手即上手。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典游戏玩法：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以扑克牌为基础，玩家依次抽取扑克牌，最接近21点的玩家则获胜，超过21点则自动爆牌输掉比赛，双方将承受对手卡牌点数差值的攻击，直至打败对手或者被对手打败。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业选择：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将选择自己的初始职业，为本场游戏的主角，每个职业都有自己的专属卡组和专属技能，并且每个职业都有两个天赋分支，每个分支都会有不同的卡牌构建。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/9fc0ce54f5dc35d226fe9632b140adad.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=665 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的肉鸽元素：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将在300多张卡牌中构建属于自己的卡牌，当然也会有偶然事件，加入新的卡牌，还是精简卡组，或者是锻造卡牌，这都将是玩家的选择，当然这些都离不开在牌桌赢下的筹码，这将是你制胜的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/5f31d3ad188ff956bd7381c19780314b.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=440 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种选择：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图采用了《杀戮尖塔》的设定，玩家将自由选择自己的遭遇战路线，每一层遇见的对手和事件都是不相同的，或许你需要特定的对手特定牌组，又或者平推到底。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/a396b5139105467329b0e5074561fbe8.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=360 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌种类，锻造升级：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/65a3b95d5c85c7477e516f55206e78ad.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=371 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先行卡背：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/3c06cc762b0c4e3fc07171cd3a717b2e.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=457 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >计划：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/40749851b16297f78c4341898e41a478.avif?t=1745051379\" width=620 height=457 /></span></p></li></ul>",
